🔷 7404 Inverter (NOT Gate)
📌 Overview
   --------
The 7404 IC contains six independent NOT gates (inverters).

A NOT gate produces the logical inverse of its input signal.

🖼️ Logic Equation
    -------------
Y = ¬A


📋Truth Table
   ----------
|   A  |    Y  |
| ---- | ----- |
| 0 🔴 | 1 🟢 |
| 1 🟢 | 0 🔴 |

 Features
 --------
* 6 independent NOT gates
* TTL-compatible operation
* +5V supply voltage
* Low propagation delay
* DIP-14 package

🎯Applications
   -----------
* Signal inversion
* Clock circuits
* Logic function simplification
* Digital control systems

